<div id="I_file">&lt;cstdio&gt;</div>
<h1>FOPEN_MAX</h1>
<div id="I_description">Potential limit of simultaneous open streams</div>
<section id="description">
This macro constant expands to an integral expression that represents the maximum number of files that can be opened simultaneously.<br>
<br>
Particular library implementations may count files opened by <samp><a href="/tmpfile">tmpfile</a></samp> towards this limit. Implementations may also allow more files to be opened beyond this limit.<br>
<br>
<samp>FOPEN_MAX</samp> shall be greater than <code>7</code> on all systems.<br>
</section>
